{"tid":1285671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[企硬] 公開會面都唔接受","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:31:55.000Z","uid":71334,"like":249,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0a55f8c89e8d1b448e8f5de45a582305b9b920","tid":1285671,"uid":71334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"閉門會面大家相信都知好鬼<br />\n但千祈唔好以為公開就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點可能一邊拉人一邊製造白色恐怖，轉過頭話可以對談？<br />\n完！全！冇！一！絲！誠！意！<br />\n五大訴求簡潔清晰，政府只得一條路，就係逐點回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會面應該係一百萬人遊行之後就做<br />\n而家佢連犧牲左嘅人命都冇回應過，仲周圍拉人<br />\n會面根本就貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d25ba6a6f4aab90dc9c9da009c308c24200a16e","tid":1285671,"uid":71334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"自推，大家唔好中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b3015355b1d1c309cb015098fbada27f9bc0dd","tid":1285671,"uid":71334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"繼續推，不接受假情假意，不接受分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca83134114828a8894af88bdd7c158af36443055","tid":1285671,"uid":71334,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"若果你猶豫，咁回顧下歷史<br />\n1、泛民密室談判<br />\n2、佔中公開會面<br />\n<br />\n請問以上邊次叫成功？<br />\n唔洗留言答，自己心入面答自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f810ae16c5a3c819231138ff72939899aade1d","tid":1285671,"uid":260035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"自己開個正常唔係播帶讀稿既記招直接回應訴求啦  訊求寫得咁清楚 係唔想答應訴求先想談判拖淡件事"},{"pid":"0142c26e877187a2af94bc01b3385b4dc39418af","tid":1285671,"uid":272716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"49ba3cc63502ce001c69e1e916e8b49e183705f4","tid":1285671,"uid":6879,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"想傾就開offer 先，回應下d 訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係你求我地傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a842ed9229b6faf8a5f9e1d1d6a8d0aae7283117","tid":1285671,"uid":71334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"唔好淨留負皮就走人，留言討論<br />\n只要有理據，極度歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯隨便插，連登唔係土共咁一言堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea50bde02fed235d2f6576289d27eec9097cccc8","tid":1285671,"uid":37232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"雖然陳雲成日唔食藥但今次OK...<br />\n大學學生會最多只可以話轉達訴求, 無得談判, 亦唔可能控制民間運動<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：切勿談判、拒絕代表、不信承諾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285599</a><br />\n<br />\n一、切勿談判：絕對不可進入任何拖延時間而令自己情緒平復及場地局部恢復日常秩序而令在場者被瓦解及司法報復的談判。不要以台灣的太陽花運動為榜樣，而那是個失敗的運動。<br />\n<br />\n二、拒絕一切代表：絕對不可以信任任何議會代表或民間代表。任何人如果代理這場談判，都會冒著難以估計的政治道德風險，因為你面對的是毫無原則的、隨時背信棄義的中共及港共。<br />\n<br />\n三、不可信任任何政府元首或政府部門的口頭承諾，這些是政府的城下之盟，他們可以隨時反悔而撲殺而毫不影響政府的道德立場。<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wan Chin<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%9B%8D%E5%B8%96%E8%A1%97-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%98%E9%81%8E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9-%E6%85%A3%E6%8A%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%259B%258D%25E5%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25AD%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E6%2585%25A3%25E6%258A%2580%2F&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=bd6fb60d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%259B%258D%25E5%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25AD%2598%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%259A%2584-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E6%2585%25A3%25E6%258A%2580%2F&h=19f9e738\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%9B%8D%E5%B8%96%E8%A1%97-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%98%E9%81%8E%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%9A%84-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9-%E6%85%A3%E6%8A%80/</a><br />\n<br />\n清拆囍帖街、佔領運動&hellip; 香港人見識過林鄭的「暫緩」慣技<br />\n<br />\n2007 年，清拆灣仔囍帖街 15 人街頭行動被捕，引起社會反響，政府及後宣佈暫緩工程，派林鄭落場與居民商討，隔了一會，推土機就繼續如常開工，最後變了今日不輪不類的囍匯。<br />\n<br />\n2014 年林鄭被派出處理佔領運動與學生對話，及後透過中間人提出有第二輪會面。但然後再沒然後，擴日持久待民意消耗，就直接走數清場終結。<br />\n<br />\n一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭，林鄭是心明此道之人。公眾往往認為暫緩執行是釋出善意，其實對於一個執行政治任務的妹仔，今次再被派出處理政治炸彈，她很清楚所有的暫緩，都是為了打散群眾訴求無誤。<br />\n<br />\n如果多年來香港人見識過這個慣犯的慣技，每次都繼續盲目相信，那麼輸掉香港的理由就是你自己，與人無尤了。"},{"pid":"320635a089d9aa4760e4cd85f1111391b381925b","tid":1285671